    "2022), Reverse Variance Learning (Bao et al. 2022), Exact Likelihood Computation (Song et al.",
    "2020; Cheng et al. 2022).",
    "To overcome the likelihood optimization ignored in diffusion models due to the intractability of log-likelihood, MLE training (Song et al. 2021; Kingma et al."
  ]
